data.description: Welcome to your charming new home with beautiful views of Butte, the Highlands, and the East Ridge! This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom house offers a wonderful blend of comfort and affordability. The main level features the kitchen, 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, and a cozy living room. The second level features 2 additional attic-style bedrooms. The unfinished basement offers plenty of space for storage as well as your laundry area. Outside, you'll find a 2-car garage, providing secure parking for your vehicles and additional storage space for your tools or outdoor equipment and a fenced yard. This house is within reach for those seeking affordability without compromising on quality of life. It's an excellent opportunity for first-time homebuyers, downsizers, or investors. Reach out today to schedule your private showing!
